==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dissilient
<hw>Dis*sil"i*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>dissiliens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>dissilire</ets>
to leap asunder: <ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>salire</ets> to leap.]</ety>
<def>Starting asunder; bursting and opening with an elastic force;
dehiscing explosively; <as>as, a <ex>dissilient</ex>
pericarp</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dissilition</ent>⟦br⟧
